OL,3,CHomelessness crisis the 'worst it has
OL,4,Cbeen for a long time'
OL,6,FBelfast's homelessness crisis is "the
OL,7,Fworst it has been for a long time", an
OL,8,Foutreach team has said.
OL,10,FServices are stretched, teams are
OL,11,Funder pressure and temporary
OL,12,Faccommodation is reportedly more
OL,13,Fdifficult to secure due to demand.
OL,15,FHomelessness in the city is not a new
OL,16,Fissue, but the streets are becoming
OL,17,Fmore dangerous.
OL,19,FEllie Hippsley is an outreach worker
OL,20,Ffor the Welcome Organisation.
