OL,3,CHomelessness crisis the 'worst it has
OL,4,Cbeen for a long time'
OL,6,FOut on patrol with UTV, she said: "The
OL,7,Fjob is supposed to be, find a person
OL,8,Fwho's experiencing street homelessness
OL,9,Fand accommodate them. That seems like
OL,10,Fa pretty simple step by step process,
OL,11,Fbut in reality, you're finding people
OL,12,Fat their absolute worst and having to
OL,13,Fbuild them up.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/7
