OL,3,CHomelessness crisis the 'worst it has
OL,4,Cbeen for a long time'
OL,6,F"We could open more temporary
OL,7,Faccommodation tomorrow, but we need to
OL,8,Fstop what's causing people to become
OL,9,Fhomeless in the first place. This is a
OL,10,Fmental health issue, a physical health
OL,11,Fissue, a criminal justice issue and a
OL,12,Fsocietal issue. This isn't just a
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland Housing Executive
OL,14,Fissue."
OL,16,FThe Welcome Organisation told us that
OL,17,Faddiction issues are exacerbating the
OL,18,Fproblem as well as a lack of temporary
OL,19,Faccommodation for rough sleepers.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/7
