OL,3,CHomelessness crisis the 'worst it has
OL,4,Cbeen for a long time'
OL,6,F"It's the worst that we've seen in a
OL,7,Flong time," Ellie said.
OL,9,FThe Welcome Organisation has recorded
OL,10,Fa 380% increase in female rough
OL,11,Fsleeping in 5 years. That's compared
OL,12,Fto a 260% increase in male rough
OL,13,Fsleeping in five years. The pressure's
OL,14,Fhigh.
OL,16,FWe spoke to one rough sleeper as we
OL,17,Fwere out with the organisation. We
OL,18,Fhave hidden his identity.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/7
