OL,3,CHomelessness crisis the 'worst it has
OL,4,Cbeen for a long time'
OL,6,FThe Northern Ireland Housing Executive
OL,7,Ftold us that it has significantly
OL,8,Fincreased the supply of suitable
OL,9,Ftemporary accommodation while dealing
OL,10,Fwith demand that has doubled over the
OL,11,Flast five years.
OL,13,FThe Department of Health said it is
OL,14,Fworking collaboratively with the
OL,15,FDepartment for Communities on an
OL,16,Faction plan to tackle homelessness.
